| What you want | `make` command     | Raw Windows command                                                                 |
| ------------- | ------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Run API       | `make run`         | `uvicorn api.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000`                          |
| Run UI        | `make ui`          | `streamlit run ui/app.py --server.port=8501 --server.address=0.0.0.0`               |
| Run MCP       | `make mcp`         | `python -m mcp_server.run`                                                          |
| Run tests     | `make test`        | `python -m pytest tests/ -v`                                                        |
| Run eval      | `make eval`        | `python -m eval.run_eval`                                                           |
| Run Docker    | `make docker`      | `docker compose up --build`                                                         |
| Stop Docker   | `make docker-down` | `docker compose down`                                                               |
| Clean         | `make clean`       | `Remove-Item -Recurse logs/*.json, eval/results/*.json, __pycache__, .pytest_cache` |
